        <span class="v2-what-is-iris__label-{{ section.id }}">III — Identity &amp; Archive</span>
        <h2 class="v2-what-is-iris__split-title-{{ section.id }}">Scan it. It becomes yours.</h2>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__copy-{{ section.id }}">
          <p>Every IRIS ships sealed. Inside the frame, an NFC chip. When you scan it, the piece identifies itself — artwork, number, rarity. First time anyone sees it. That scan also registers your piece as authentic. It enters the archive. From that moment, it has a record, a place, an owner.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__identity-visual-{{ section.id }} v2-what-is-iris__identity-visual-{{ section.id }}--bleed" id="V2WhatIsIrisIdentityVisual-{{ section.id }}">
