          <p>Hold your phone to the NFC chip and enter your unique PIN code. In that single moment — artwork, number, rarity, archive entry. Everything at once. This is the moment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-num-{{ section.id }}">03</div>
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-title-{{ section.id }}">It is yours</div>
          <p>Your piece enters the permanent archive under your name. Its record cannot be altered. The number belongs to you.</p>
